Dialogue: 2,0:01:27.62,0:01:38.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}即使胸中苦闷 去感受真切的现在吧{\fad(0,400)}
Dialogue: 2,0:01:39.63,0:01:42.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}比外表更单纯
Dialogue: 2,0:01:43.43,0:01:46.27,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}可是却无法传达
Dialogue: 2,0:01:47.10,0:01:53.84,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想要说的话 总是藏在口袋里
Dialogue: 2,0:01:54.45,0:02:00.31,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}充满孩子气的话语 如今已无法开口
Dialogue: 2,0:02:01.79,0:02:08.35,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}虽说时间会冲淡一切 我们却无法相互理解
Dialogue: 2,0:02:08.35,0:02:14.58,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}24小时 一直相信着你
Dialogue: 2,0:02:15.60,0:02:18.36,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看着你
Dialogue: 2,0:02:19.37,0:02:23.04,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}即使只是俗常的话语
Dialogue: 2,0:02:23.34,0:02:29.41,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}时间总是 微笑着匆匆流逝
Dialogue: 2,0:02:30.48,0:02:41.26,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}比起回忆 还是去追求理想的今天{\fad(0,1025)}
Dialogue: 2,0:03:04.79,0:03:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:03:06.09,0:03:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}又从哪里搞来一只新的手啦
Dialogue: 2,0:03:08.82,0:03:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这只借来的手臂
Dialogue: 2,0:03:10.91,0:03:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}能挡住铁碎牙的结界
Dialogue: 2,0:03:14.53,0:03:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那是龙的手
Dialogue: 2,0:03:16.66,0:03:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}咦？
Dialogue: 2,0:03:18.17,0:03:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}比普通妖怪的手臂要结实很多
Dialogue: 2,0:03:22.57,0:03:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他想用那只手臂做什么呢…
Dialogue: 2,0:03:26.44,0:03:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}管你是龙的手臂还是什么
Dialogue: 2,0:03:28.94,0:03:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只要碰到刀身
Dialogue: 2,0:03:30.45,0:03:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}同样也会伤得不轻吧
Dialogue: 2,0:03:34.58,0:03:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不愧是铁碎牙
Dialogue: 2,0:03:37.19,0:03:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}即使使用它的人是个废物
Dialogue: 2,0:03:39.05,0:03:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}龙之腕也未必挡得住
Dialogue: 2,0:03:41.29,0:03:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是
Dialogue: 2,0:03:42.69,0:03:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}既然使用者能受到结界承认
Dialogue: 2,0:03:45.23,0:03:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为何没有传授“风之伤”
Dialogue: 2,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}铁碎牙呀
Dialogue: 2,0:03:49.76,0:03:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}撕裂虚空 让我见识你的真正力量吧
Dialogue: 2,0:03:54.57,0:03:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哇…杀生丸能看见「风之伤」
Dialogue: 2,0:03:58.81,0:04:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}老爷爷 「风之伤」是什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:01.78,0:04:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}简单的说 那就是能够发挥铁碎牙力量的奥义
Dialogue: 2,0:04:07.08,0:04:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要想一次消灭上百只妖怪
Dialogue: 2,0:04:09.28,0:04:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就必须能够看见「风之伤」
Dialogue: 2,0:04:12.79,0:04:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸就能看到它
Dialogue: 2,0:04:15.52,0:04:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那也把那奥义教给犬夜叉吧 现在马上
Dialogue: 2,0:04:19.76,0:04:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是无法传授的
Dialogue: 2,0:04:22.26,0:04:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}必须由犬夜叉自己领悟才行
Dialogue: 2,0:04:25.27,0:04:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果他做不到的话…
Dialogue: 2,0:04:27.57,0:04:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}犬夜叉就会死在这里
Dialogue: 2,0:04:31.24,0:04:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}名刀选择的真正主人
Dialogue: 2,0:04:48.82,0:04:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}竟然用蛮力打过来…
Dialogue: 2,0:05:04.94,0:05:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}犬夜叉
Dialogue: 2,0:05:12.31,0:05:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}刀在鸣泣？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:14.58,0:05:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸是不是
Dialogue: 2,0:05:15.88,0:05:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}针对铁碎牙而来的呢
Dialogue: 2,0:05:18.89,0:05:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}糟糕了
Dialogue: 2,0:05:20.09,0:05:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他一味看准振动的波峰来攻击
Dialogue: 2,0:05:23.29,0:05:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就算是铁碎牙 如此持续下去
Dialogue: 2,0:05:26.46,0:05:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也会被打断的
Dialogue: 2,0:05:30.16,0:05:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这家伙怎么回事？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:36.47,0:05:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸在和铁碎牙战斗…
Dialogue: 2,0:05:47.12,0:05:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}犬夜叉
Dialogue: 2,0:05:49.12,0:05:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别过来
Dialogue: 2,0:05:52.12,0:05:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不要插手
Dialogue: 2,0:05:53.86,0:05:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸由我来…
Dialogue: 2,0:05:55.76,0:05:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}用铁碎牙干掉！
Dialogue: 2,0:05:58.63,0:06:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这家伙的目标是打断铁碎牙
Dialogue: 2,0:06:02.36,0:06:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谁会眼睁睁让他得逞啊！
Dialogue: 2,0:06:07.87,0:06:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}犬夜叉虽然只有一次
Dialogue: 2,0:06:10.64,0:06:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但还是发挥过铁碎牙的真正力量
Dialogue: 2,0:06:13.15,0:06:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}即使那是偶然
Dialogue: 2,0:06:14.94,0:06:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果没有天份的话 还是使不出来的
Dialogue: 2,0:06:17.88,0:06:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}可是
Dialogue: 2,0:06:18.88,0:06:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要是这次无法施展的话会被杀的…
Dialogue: 2,0:06:22.65,0:06:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}犬夜叉
Dialogue: 2,0:06:24.89,0:06:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}无法发威吗 铁碎牙
Dialogue: 2,0:06:27.16,0:06:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么就跟你的主人一起死吧
Dialogue: 2,0:06:44.47,0:06:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这家伙 在保护刀吗
Dialogue: 2,0:06:48.81,0:06:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嘿嘿 还没能运用自如的刀
Dialogue: 2,0:06:52.68,0:06:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎能让你就这样毁了它
Dialogue: 2,0:07:13.50,0:07:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}可恶 看不见了
Dialogue: 2,0:07:18.71,0:07:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}妖气
Dialogue: 2,0:07:24.58,0:07:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看见了！妖气的漩涡！
Dialogue: 2,0:07:29.35,0:07:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}风互相磨擦的味道
Dialogue: 2,0:07:32.45,0:07:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是妖气流相撞产生的裂缝
Dialogue: 2,0:07:35.79,0:07:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不是！是风的味道！
Dialogue: 2,0:07:43.23,0:07:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在那里
Dialogue: 2,0:08:34.48,0:08:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}结束了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:37.52,0:08:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}啊 那就是风之伤啊
Dialogue: 2,0:08:41.09,0:08:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}太好了 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 2,0:08:43.09,0:08:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听说那是发挥铁碎牙真正力量的奥义哦
Dialogue: 2,0:08:46.99,0:08:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸死了吗
Dialogue: 2,0:08:49.23,0:08:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}可能因为他被铁碎牙真正的剑压击中了啊
Dialogue: 2,0:08:55.87,0:08:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么真正的剑压
Dialogue: 2,0:08:58.01,0:09:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只是被毒迷了眼睛痛苦地乱挥刀子罢了
Dialogue: 2,0:09:04.01,0:09:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你说什么？臭老头
Dialogue: 2,0:09:06.81,0:09:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}算了 听好
Dialogue: 2,0:09:07.88,0:09:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你能嗅出风之伤值得称赞
Dialogue: 2,0:09:11.12,0:09:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}可是这只代表你终于能跟杀生丸一样了
Dialogue: 2,0:09:16.09,0:09:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不…应该是那家伙变弱了吧
Dialogue: 2,0:09:21.10,0:09:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这话是什么意思呢
Dialogue: 2,0:09:23.90,0:09:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}刚才的打斗中
Dialogue: 2,0:09:25.53,0:09:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}天生牙保住了杀生丸的性命
Dialogue: 2,0:09:30.64,0:09:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}天生牙保住他的命？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸没有死吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:39.65,0:09:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}犬夜叉
Dialogue: 2,0:09:40.92,0:09:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你应该也没有感受到砍到杀生丸的手感吧
Dialogue: 2,0:09:46.15,0:09:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是这样吗 犬夜叉？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:49.26,0:09:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嗯 那家伙的气息
Dialogue: 2,0:09:52.06,0:09:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}从铁碎牙放出的光芒当中消失了
Dialogue: 2,0:09:55.66,0:09:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不过不是被轰飞出去
Dialogue: 2,0:09:57.67,0:09:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}感觉像是突然消失了一般
Dialogue: 2,0:10:03.77,0:10:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}天生牙从犬夜叉发出的剑压中保护了杀生丸
Dialogue: 2,0:10:10.31,0:10:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一切都是天生牙自己的判断
Dialogue: 2,0:10:13.68,0:10:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}天生牙的判断？
Dialogue: 2,0:10:15.78,0:10:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}天生牙是拯救性命的治愈之刀
Dialogue: 2,0:10:20.19,0:10:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因此杀生丸痛恨这把刀
Dialogue: 2,0:10:24.19,0:10:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是当杀生丸遭遇危险时
Dialogue: 2,0:10:27.96,0:10:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}无关主人的意志
Dialogue: 2,0:10:30.10,0:10:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}天生牙拯救了杀生丸 是这个意思吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:10:34.70,0:10:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这种敌人要怎么打倒 我一点办法都没有
Dialogue: 2,0:10:46.71,0:10:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}反正刀已经磨好了
Dialogue: 2,0:10:49.48,0:10:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今后你就多多修行以打倒杀生丸和天生牙吧
Dialogue: 2,0:10:56.82,0:10:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸跟犬夜叉
Dialogue: 2,0:10:59.26,0:11:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们的父亲给了他们一人一把刀
Dialogue: 2,0:11:03.53,0:11:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}天生牙跟铁碎牙
Dialogue: 2,0:11:06.13,0:11:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那是不是说不准他们兄弟打架呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:11:12.77,0:11:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}算了 他们早晚会领悟的
Dialogue: 2,0:12:32.59,0:12:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别做多余的事情
Dialogue: 2,0:12:34.96,0:12:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}人类的食物不合我胃口
Dialogue: 2,0:12:54.81,0:12:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}果然没错
Dialogue: 2,0:12:57.33,0:12:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}铃 犯人原来就是你
Dialogue: 2,0:13:00.11,0:13:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}竟然敢偷抓鱼池里的鱼
Dialogue: 2,0:13:04.15,0:13:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看你无依无靠很可怜
Dialogue: 2,0:13:06.65,0:13:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}才让村子里的人扶养你的
Dialogue: 2,0:13:08.99,0:13:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}下次敢再这样就打死你
Dialogue: 2,0:13:13.23,0:13:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真是的 阴阳怪气的小鬼
Dialogue: 2,0:13:15.63,0:13:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}连哭一声都不会
Dialogue: 2,0:13:17.90,0:13:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那也难怪了
Dialogue: 2,0:13:19.53,0:13:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}自从亲眼看到父母兄弟被山贼杀害后
Dialogue: 2,0:13:22.17,0:13:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}她就无法开口说话了
Dialogue: 2,0:13:36.68,0:13:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不需要
Dialogue: 2,0:13:42.42,0:13:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我说了我什么都不要
Dialogue: 2,0:13:51.00,0:13:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}脸上的伤怎么回事
Dialogue: 2,0:13:59.21,0:14:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不想说就算了
Dialogue: 2,0:14:11.55,0:14:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有什么好高兴的
Dialogue: 2,0:14:14.32,0:14:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我只是问你的状况而已
Dialogue: 2,0:14:44.62,0:14:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么
Dialogue: 2,0:14:46.32,0:14:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这破烂小屋是你家呀？
Dialogue: 2,0:14:51.36,0:14:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哇！是狼 狼啊！
Dialogue: 2,0:14:55.23,0:14:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}啊 已经追来了啊
Dialogue: 2,0:15:03.74,0:15:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}可恶
Dialogue: 2,0:15:20.48,0:15:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}找得我好苦
Dialogue: 2,0:15:21.96,0:15:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个臭小偷！
Dialogue: 2,0:15:25.16,0:15:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好了
Dialogue: 2,0:15:25.89,0:15:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}乖乖交出你偷走的四魂碎片吧
Dialogue: 2,0:15:29.96,0:15:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我知道了 我不会再逃了
Dialogue: 2,0:15:41.61,0:15:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}感激不尽 您要饶我一命吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:50.65,0:15:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}笨蛋 我是忘了
Dialogue: 2,0:15:53.99,0:15:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好了 工作结束 我先回去了
Dialogue: 2,0:15:58.39,0:16:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}村民就让你们吃个痛快吧
Dialogue: 2,0:16:26.72,0:16:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}戈薇 你怎么了？
Dialogue: 2,0:16:28.66,0:16:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}从刚刚开始就沉默不语
Dialogue: 2,0:16:31.06,0:16:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嗯 虽然很微弱
Dialogue: 2,0:16:33.33,0:16:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我感觉到了四魂碎片的气息
Dialogue: 2,0:16:36.20,0:16:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真的吗？戈薇
Dialogue: 2,0:16:37.87,0:16:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在哪个方向？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:13.87,0:17:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 2,0:17:17.74,0:17:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸大人 请您回答我
Dialogue: 2,0:17:21.74,0:17:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}您在哪里？杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 2,0:17:25.28,0:17:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸大人该不会
Dialogue: 2,0:17:27.25,0:17:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}被犬夜叉「唰」地一下砍死了吧…
Dialogue: 2,0:17:31.59,0:17:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}「唰」地一下？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:33.25,0:17:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}提到这个
Dialogue: 2,0:17:36.52,0:17:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那时杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 2,0:17:38.89,0:17:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}毫不犹豫拔刀砍向了我
Dialogue: 2,0:17:46.30,0:17:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还说天生牙是无法杀人的刀
Dialogue: 2,0:17:49.54,0:17:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}难道是拿我邪见试刀吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:55.98,0:17:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拿我试刀 其实不是
Dialogue: 2,0:17:59.21,0:18:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拿我试刀 其实不是
Dialogue: 2,0:18:02.18,0:18:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拿我试刀 其实不是
Dialogue: 2,0:18:05.89,0:18:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拿我试刀…拿我试刀？
Dialogue: 2,0:18:09.76,0:18:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 2,0:18:11.39,0:18:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那时候我死了您也觉得无所谓吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:18:14.60,0:18:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 2,0:18:22.24,0:18:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}啊 杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 2,0:18:25.41,0:18:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 2,0:18:26.74,0:18:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}您当时真的是拿邪见试刀吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:18:30.78,0:18:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不是因为挂念我
Dialogue: 2,0:18:32.91,0:18:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}才来找我的吗
Dialogue: 2,0:18:35.58,0:18:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那…那个…杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 2,0:18:38.82,0:18:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}您平安无事真是太好了…
Dialogue: 2,0:18:47.09,0:18:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}血 还有狼的味道
Dialogue: 2,0:18:51.50,0:18:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这股血的味道是…
Dialogue: 2,0:19:10.12,0:19:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么回事？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:11.95,0:19:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}唉呀 这样子已经没救了
Dialogue: 2,0:19:14.12,0:19:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}应该是狼吧 被狼咬死的
Dialogue: 2,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 2,0:19:20.63,0:19:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}您认识这个人类吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:31.10,0:19:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}啊 杀生丸大人…
Dialogue: 2,0:19:41.48,0:19:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}原来如此
Dialogue: 2,0:19:43.48,0:19:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我看到了
Dialogue: 2,0:19:45.99,0:19:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这些家伙是「那个」世界的使者吧
Dialogue: 2,0:19:50.49,0:19:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}来试试看吧  天生牙的力量
Dialogue: 2,0:19:54.70,0:19:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}试…试试看？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:56.93,0:19:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 2,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}您刚才说什么…
Dialogue: 2,0:20:22.46,0:20:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}活过来了
Dialogue: 2,0:20:24.12,0:20:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那个…杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 2,0:20:26.23,0:20:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸大人用天生牙救了那个女孩？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:32.97,0:20:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀…杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 2,0:20:36.94,0:20:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸大人居然会拯救人类
Dialogue: 2,0:20:40.64,0:20:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}实在让人太惊讶了
Dialogue: 2,0:20:42.38,0:20:43.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}刚才杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 2,0:20:44.18,0:20:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}的确说过了「来试试看吧」
Dialogue: 2,0:20:48.48,0:20:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这…这么说…
Dialogue: 2,0:20:49.72,0:20:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我果然是为了试刀才被砍的…
Dialogue: 2,0:20:53.49,0:20:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸大人…邪见太伤心了…
Dialogue: 2,0:20:57.36,0:21:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好伤心…邪见好伤心…杀生丸大人太过分了
Dialogue: 2,0:21:07.57,0:21:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杀生丸大人请等等我
Dialogue: 2,0:21:11.00,0:21:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哼 天生牙吗
Dialogue: 2,0:21:15.38,0:21:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让我救了人类吗
Dialogue: 2,0:21:22.52,0:21:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 2,0:21:23.75,0:21:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}喂 有人在吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:21:26.52,0:21:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是兽群的杰作
Dialogue: 2,0:21:28.29,0:21:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是狼的足迹
Dialogue: 2,0:21:30.49,0:21:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}数量不在少数
Dialogue: 2,0:21:32.59,0:21:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}戈薇小姐感觉到的四魂碎片是…
Dialogue: 2,0:21:36.26,0:21:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有可能
Dialogue: 2,0:21:37.50,0:21:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这一定又是妖怪下的毒手
Dialogue: 2,0:21:45.61,0:21:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}出现了！ 是…是吃人的野狼
Dialogue: 2,0:21:53.78,0:21:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哼 很有种嘛
Dialogue: 2,0:21:57.05,0:21:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只会以多欺少 一群没用的家伙
Dialogue: 2,0:22:00.12,0:22:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}通通解决掉免得烦人
Dialogue: 2,0:22:10.03,0:22:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}散魂铁爪
Dialogue: 2,0:22:20.21,0:22:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哇 它们在嚎叫
Dialogue: 2,0:22:22.54,0:22:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是在呼叫同伴
Dialogue: 2,0:22:31.79,0:22:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}啊 四魂碎片的气息接近了
Dialogue: 2,0:22:35.16,0:22:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而且 速度好快
Dialogue: 2,0:22:54.81,0:22:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有男人从风里出来了
Dialogue: 2,0:23:02.82,0:23:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你们
Dialogue: 2,0:23:07.39,0:23:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么杀了我的手下
Dialogue: 2,0:23:11.12,0:23:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个人右手和双腿上都有四魂碎片…
Dialogue: 2,0:23:17.30,0:23:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你就是这些家伙的头领吗
Dialogue: 2,0:23:31.72,0:23:37.25,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们 在生命的旅程中{\fad(400,0)}
Dialogue: 2,0:23:37.75,0:23:43.25,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}渐渐地 失去所有
Dialogue: 2,0:23:43.70,0:23:49.07,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我仍坚信着 追逐着光明
Dialogue: 2,0:23:49.70,0:23:56.25,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在与你 一同出发{\fad(0,1050)}
Dialogue: 2,0:24:01.10,0:24:06.30,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如今在那深深的丛林中
Dialogue: 2,0:24:06.55,0:24:12.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也一定埋藏着 被丢弃的心
Dialogue: 2,0:24:13.45,0:24:18.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}若能把握时光的轮回
Dialogue: 2,0:24:18.62,0:24:25.17,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也许 能再次飞翔{\fad(0,1050)}
Dialogue: 2,0:24:28.30,0:24:33.55,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们将彷徨着
Dialogue: 2,0:24:34.05,0:24:40.06,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}生存下去 直到永远
Dialogue: 2,0:24:40.12,0:24:45.52,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}仍然坚信着 追逐着光明
Dialogue: 2,0:24:45.92,0:24:52.47,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在与你 一同出发{\fad(0,1000)}
